These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: italian, egyptian, british, malaysian
1. Nationality:egyptian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:malaysian is between Nationality:italian and Nationality:egyptian##2
3. Nationality:malaysian is on the right of Nationality:italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | italian | malaysian | egyptian | british |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: asparagus, pumpkin, nectarine, pineapple
1. Food:asparagus is on the left of Food:pineapple##1
2. Food:pumpkin is in an odd position##4
3. Food:pumpkin is on the left or right of Food:asparagus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | pumpkin | asparagus | pineapple | nectarine |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: crime, superhero, animation, horror
1. Movie-Genre:horror is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:crime##3
2. Movie-Genre:crime is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:animation is between Movie-Genre:horror and Movie-Genre:superhero##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | horror | animation | superhero |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
