.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: orange, potato, pomegranate, cucumber
1. Food:potato == Food:potato##1
2. Food:cucumber is on the left or right of Food:pomegranate##3
3. Food:pomegranate is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:orange is in an even position##4
5. Food:cucumber is on the left of Food:potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | pomegranate | cucumber | potato | orange |

